          <div class="cosmic-card" style="padding: 24px; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 36px; display: block; margin-bottom: 12px;">ü¶†</span><h3 class="space-font" style="color: var(--solar-orange); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 8px;">VIRUS REMOVAL</h3><p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--comet-silver); font-size: 13px;">Complete malware removal, security cleanup, system optimisation.</p></div>
          <div class="cosmic-card" style="padding: 24px; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 36px; display: block; margin-bottom: 12px;">üíæ</span><h3 class="space-font" style="color: var(--nebula-purple); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 8px;">DATA RECOVERY</h3><p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--comet-silver); font-size: 13px;">Failed hard drive? We recover photos, documents, and important files.</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section-bg" style="padding: 60px 0;">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="cosmic-card" style="padding: 40px;">
          <h2 class="space-font" style="color: var(--plasma-cyan); font-size: clamp(20px, 4vw, 28px); margin-bottom: 24px;">YOUR LOCAL {area.name.toUpperCase()} COMPUTER EXPERT</h2>
          <p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--starlight-white); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 20px;">
            Serving {area.name} and the wider {area.region} borough, we're just {area.distance} away in Harold Hill. Whether you're near {area.landmarks.join(", ")}, we offer fast collection and delivery for your convenience.
          </p>
          <p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--comet-silver); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 24px;">
